These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, tram, snowmobile, boat, taxi, subway, motorbike
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, rose, daffodil, marigold, azalea, begonia, tulip
 1. the person who growstulip is the person driving the boat##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
 4. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
 5. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
 6. the person driving the bus is not the person who growsrose##6
 7. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 9. the person who growsazalea is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growsrose##7
10. the person who growsrose is the person driving the subway##1
11. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
12. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
13. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsamaryllis##7
15. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
16. the person who growsbegonia is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
17. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
18. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growsdaffodil##1
19. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
20. the person driving the boat is not the person who growsbegonia##6
21. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
22. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Transport           | subway | snowmobile | motorbike | tram  | taxi  | boat | bus    |
| Flower   | rose   | amaryllis   | daffodil   | marigold | azalea | tulip        | begonia |

