 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes red is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
10. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes red##1
11. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
13. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
14. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
15. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
